    "from tensorflow.keras.callbacks import EarlyStopping\n",
    "f.manual_forecast(call_me='lstm_24lags_earlystop_3layers',\n",
    "                  lags=24,\n",
    "                  epochs=25,\n",
    "                  validation_split=.2,\n",
    "                  shuffle=True,\n",
    "                  callbacks=EarlyStopping(monitor='val_loss',\n",
    "                                          patience=5),\n",
    "                  lstm_layer_sizes=(16,16,16),\n",
    "                  dropout=(0,0,0))\n",
    "f.plot_test_set(ci=True)"
   ]
  },
